I go to this Starbucks a lot due to its proximity to my school, but it is rarely an enjoyable experience. The service is slow and extremely inconsistent, with some custom drinks being made quicker than a cup of tea or coffee in spite of them being ordered at the same time. The servers are inconsistent as well, with some being very helpful and others being annoyed when you ask a question about you order or ask for the milk to be refilled. I have seen them make orders for friends and other workers from surrounding stores before those of people that ordered and paid on multiple occasions. Furthermore, the nitro cold brew is basically always out to a point where it may as well not be on the menu.  If you are near this Starbucks, I highly recommend thinking of other alternatives, or ordering ahead since those orders are generally made more timely.
